snippet.title: Coleco Telstar Alpha - Hockey & Hidden Game (AY-3-8500-1)
snippet.description:
Hockey game and also the hidden game (extra bat on right player's side) on the Coleco Telstar Alpha (A/V modded) dedicated console. This video was made March 04, 2015 with an Adesso video capture (model AV-200).

To get the hidden game, just position the game switch between two games. In reality, this is a bug that appears (the extra bat) when no game is selected since the bat from the Jai Alai (squash) game becomes fonctional in the hockey game.
